Class pnmlReader

java.lang.Object
propra.pnml.PNMLWopedParser
propra.pnml.pnmlReader
public class pnmlReader extends propra.pnml.PNMLWopedParser
The pnmlReader class extends PNMLWopedParser and is responsible for parsing PNML files into Petrinet objects.
